---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TedaviDoktorlari from '../../../components/TedaviDoktorlari.astro';

// SEO Title and Description
const pageTitle = "E-Max and Empress Porcelain Teeth | Transparent Aesthetics | Yuceler A+ Clinic";
const pageDescription = "Full ceramic (metal-free) E-max and Empress dental crown treatments in Silivri and Catalca. Natural, transparent, and flawless smile design with maximum light transmittance.";
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/empress-banner.webp');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-klinik-koyu/95 via-klinik-koyu/60 to-transparent z-0"></div> 
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-yesil text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Maximum Transparency</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-2xl">
          Natural and Flawless <br/><span class="text-klinik-yesil">E-Max & Empress Porcelain</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
          Achieve aesthetics that rival natural teeth on your front teeth with E-Max crowns made entirely of reinforced glass ceramic, containing no metal infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">What is E-Max and Empress Porcelain?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            E-Max (Lithium Disilicate) and Empress crowns are aesthetic dentistry applications consisting entirely of reinforced porcelain (glass ceramic) without any metal infrastructure inside. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            They are the materials whose light transmittance is closest to natural tooth enamel. Thanks to these features, they provide the most perfect and natural aesthetic results, especially in the <strong>restoration of anterior teeth</strong>, smile design applications, and single tooth crowns. They do not cause a gray or purplish discoloration at the gingival margin.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-klinik-yesil mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">What are the Advantages of E-Max / Empress Porcelain?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Superior Aesthetics:</strong> Transmits light just like a natural tooth, does not create an artificial or matte appearance.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Minimum Abrasion:</strong> Because it adheres very well to the tooth tissue, it allows less material to be removed from the tooth.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Biocompatible:</strong> Does not cause allergic reactions as it contains no metal; it is 100% compatible with the gums.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Low Plaque Retention:</strong> Because its surface is extremely smooth, tartar and stain accumulation on it is minimal.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">How Does the E-Max Treatment Process Work?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Digital Analysis and Preparation</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">First, your face and smile analysis is performed. Your teeth are minimally shaped under local anesthesia, and a digital impression is taken with 3D intraoral scanners.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Temporary Tooth Application</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Immediately after the impression is taken, aesthetic temporary crowns are placed on your teeth in the same session. Thus, your aesthetic appearance is preserved and tooth sensitivity is prevented during the laboratory phase.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Laboratory and Delivery</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">E-Max restorations, produced by milling with computer-aided CAD/CAM systems, are permanently integrated into your tooth with special light-cured chemical adhesives after an intraoral rehearsal.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 sticky top-32">
          <img src="/images/empress-kutu.webp" alt="E-Max Porcelain Treatment" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-t-2xl shadow-sm" />
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-b-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Take Your Smile to Hollywood Standards</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 text-sm">Let's create your personalized aesthetic porcelain treatment plan right away with a free digital analysis.</p>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.031 21.033c-1.56 0-3.084-.42-4.42-1.216l-.317-.189-3.284.861.876-3.203-.207-.331a9.022 9.022 0 0 1-1.378-4.755C3.301 7.155 7.215 3.24 12.031 3.24c2.33 0 4.519.907 6.166 2.555 1.648 1.648 2.556 3.837 2.556 6.167 0 4.914-3.915 8.829-8.73 8.829z" /></svg>
              Ask Price via WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+902124000013" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-klinik-koyu text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
              Call Clinic: +90 212 400 00 13
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TedaviDoktorlari tedavi="empress-porselen" />

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="text-klinik-yesil">Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Things you might wonder about E-Max and Empress Porcelain.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Should Zirconium or E-Max porcelain be preferred?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Both are metal-free materials that provide excellent aesthetics. However, <strong>E-Max has higher light transmittance than zirconium</strong>, so E-Max is preferred especially for <strong>anterior (front) teeth</strong> because it offers a more natural transparency. For <strong>posterior molars</strong> where chewing force is very high, or in long bridge treatments, Zirconium is preferred due to its durability.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Are E-Max crowns durable, do they break?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Yes, they are highly durable. E-Max is a glass ceramic reinforced with lithium disilicate. Since it adheres to the tooth enamel extremely strongly, it resists normal chewing forces for many years.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            How many days does E-Max treatment take?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Thanks to digital dentistry (CAD/CAM) protocols, E-Max treatments are concluded very quickly. The treatment is usually completed within 5 to 7 days (average of 3 sessions), including the clinical and laboratory processes.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-klinik-koyu text-white py-12 border-t-4 border-klinik-turuncu mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-klinik-turuncu font-bold text-lg mb-3">Legal Notice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          This website has been prepared solely for the purpose of informing patients, in full compliance with the Ministry of Health regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-left md:text-right">
        <p class="mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dental Implant Clinic A Plus</p>
        <p class="mb-1">Call Center: <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">+90 212 400 00 13</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg inline-block text-left border border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs">Last Updated: <span class="text-white font-bold">21.02.2026</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs">Editor: <a href="mailto:info@dentalimplanttrakya.com" class="text-klinik-turuncu hover:underline">info@dentalimplanttrakya.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="h-16 md:hidden block"></div>

</MainLayout>